<plot>Quitting Is For Losers is an office comedy set in the 1980's about the sad sack of a man known as Oleg Kennedy. Trapped in a dead-end job, the only joy he finds in life is in his cigarettes. However, when his work place becomes a "No Smoking" building, Oleg decides that it's time to give up his habit. Friends, co-workers, his boss, and even his own mother become obstacles to achieving his goal. Hilarity ensues.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?452294</url></doc>
